  text:
  - 'After many interviews, quiz, and free labor you finally manage to get the position. '
  - 'But even with the J*b that was acquired you still did not make enough income '
  - 'You made enough to pay your rent for an extra week but afterwords you where
    kicked out.  '
  - 'The money was barely enough to pay for your own food which was just enough to
    keep you alive.  '
